with courage and conviction, and extend to her our heartfelt wishes for a happy and fulfilling
retirement and every continued success in her future endeavors.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, that an appropriate copy of this resolution be prepared
for presentation with this final clause omitted from such copy.
